translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,7,"Haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log humse milne ki tawaqqu (umeed) nahin rakhte aur duniya ki zindagi hi par razi aur mutmaeen ho gaye hain, aur jo log hamari nishaniyon se gafil hain"
  10,8,Unka aakhri thikana jahannum hoga un buraiyon ki padash mein jinka iktisab woh (apne is galat aqeede aur galat tarz-e-amal ki wajah se) karte rahey
  10,9,Aur yeh bhi haeeqat hai ke jo log iman laye (yani jinhon ne un sadaqaton ko qabool karliya jo is kitab mein pesh ki gayi hain) aur neik amal karte rahey unhein unka Rubb unke iman ki wajah se seedhi raah chalayega. Niyamat bhari jannaton mein unke nichey nehrein bahengi
  10,10,"Wahan unki sada(pukar/awaz) yeh hogi ke “paak hai tu aey khuda”, unki dua yeh hogi ke “salamati ho: aur unki har baat ka khatma is par hoga ke “saari tareef Allah Rabbul Aalameen hi ke liye hai”"
  10,11,"Agar kahin Allah logon ke saath bura maamla karne mein bhi itni hi jaldi karta jitni woh duniya ki bhalayi maangne mein jaldi karte hain to unki mohlat e amal kabhi ki khatam kardi gayi hoti, (magar hamara yeh tareeqa nahin hai). Is liye hum un logon ko jo humse milne ki tawaqqu nahin rakhte unki sarkashi mein bhatakne ke liye chooth de detay hain"
  10,12,"Insan ka haal yeh hai ke jab uspar koi sakht waqt aata hai to khade aur baithey aur letay (lying) humko pukarta hai, magar jab hum uski museebat taal dete hain to aisa chal naikalta hai ke goya usne kabhi apne kisi buray waqt par humko pukara hi na tha. Is tarah hadd se guzar janey walon ke liye unke kartoot khushnuma bana diye gaye hain"
  10,13,"Logon, Tumse pehle ki qaumon ko ( jo apne apne zamane mein bar sar e urooj thi) humne halaak kardiya jab unhon ne zulm ki rawish ikhtiyar ki aur unke Rasool unke paas khuli khuli nishaniyan lekar aaye aur unhon ne iman laa kar hi na diya. Is tarah hum mujreemon ko unke jarayim (crime) ka badla diya karte hain"
  10,14,Ab unke baad humne tumko zameen mein unki jagah di hai taa-ke dekhein tum kaise amal karte ho